{"type":"message","id":"fb497c24","parentId":"f45f9bab","timestamp":"2026-05-21T19:23:34.205Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"2e67b688-2ca7-470f-9e7e-167fc45f2370","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"eed19f73ec82653ce8c952ef85504f65d12b9d668dff2058120971994b6d8da5\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-13.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 30,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6184196983807188,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 2026-05-13 Daily Log (continued)\\n\\n## Afternoon/Evening Session\\n\\n### Completed\\n- **Dashboard redesign (T-119)** — 3-column layout: Left=live activity feed, Center=Spacestation rooms, Right=quick actions\\n- **Task detail panel** — Changed from right-slide to centered modal\\n- **Dreaming toggle** — Proper on/off toggle with visual state indicator in QuickActions\\n- **Scheduler page** — Shows all OpenClaw cron jobs with on/off toggle switches\\n- **Telegram delivery fixed** — All cron jobs now deliver to chat ID 7507878944\\n- **Backup path fixed** — Changed from /Volumes/OpenClaw-WD to /Volumes/Public-1/openclaw-agent-backup\\n- **openclaw CLI path fixed** — Full path /opt/homebrew/bin/openclaw in ser\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-13.md#L1-L30\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-13.md#L1-L30\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"2f174eb618bbf41a3518bb221163595f586692e013765ba7871c2c99ca7eed37\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 162,\n      \"endLine\": 177,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6904935817274054,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Rewrote `AgentOffice.tsx` to use live OpenClaw data via `getAgentStatus` + `getSystemStats`\\n- Added ambient fallback mode (gentle random activity when no live data)\\n- New `AgentTravel.tsx`: L-shaped hallway traversal, SVG collaboration links, data-stream pulses\\n- New `DoorAnimation.tsx`: sliding doors with glow edge + air hiss effect\\n- New `AmbientStation.tsx`: ship fly-bys, chatter ticker, mood lighting, twinkling stars\\n- Updated `live-data.ts` to derive station mood/alert/queue pressure from real data\\n- Enhanced `station-state.ts` TICK with auto-decay and stale incident cleanup\\n- Build: clean, no errors. Pushed to GitHub.\\n\\n### Still pending\\n- Higher-quality room art (need HTML files from\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-15.md#L162-L177\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md#L162-L177\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"3716807f92cbc20a8da5affcede7c944fd33f807263df8552fe978c678c6244b\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 139,\n      \"endLine\": 165,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6735922841212932,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Root cause: `server.ts` used `execSync` (child_process) which is stubbed in Cloudflare Workers runtime\\n- Fix: Replaced `execSync` calls with direct `fs` reads/writes to `~/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json` and `jobs-state.json`\\n- Cron enable/disable now writes directly to `jobs.json` instead of using CLI\\n- `vite dev` serves API routes correctly (unlike `wrangler dev` which uses unenv stubs)\\n\\n### Investigate → Task Flow\\n- Investigate button on Scheduler Error Feed now auto-creates an \\\"In Progress\\\" task\\n- Task includes error details, cron job info, and is tagged with `errorId`\\n- Completing an error-linked task automatically updates cron error status to \\\"completed\\\"\\n- Error disappears from the feed on\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-15.md#L139-L165\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md#L139-L165\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"1271d93a7026a4cd95c641bab106d79dbc92ce77435dc4e3e3a3be933a4b74f1\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 21,\n      \"endLine\": 54,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6241654542128333,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Framer Motion for all JS animations (no game engine)\\n- CSS keyframes for ambient effects (terminal flicker, star twinkle)\\n- SVG animateMotion for task flow packets (lightweight, no JS loop)\\n- Event-driven state via `stationReducer` — all visual changes triggered by real state transitions\\n- Demo mode cycles: working → collaboration → incident → resolve (loops every 25s)\\n- GPU-composited transforms only (no layout thrashing)\\n\\n### Agent states implemented\\n- **Idle**: dimmed room, low monitor activity, subtle sprite pulse\\n- **Working**: brighter room, active terminal lines, radar sweep, sprite scale animation\\n- **Collaborating**: agent walks hallway to another room, collaboration link line app\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-15.md#L21-L54\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md#L21-L54\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"56403eafe473eaf95291ff486c23e65ea97505606f39c2596278ad8eeb1ec017\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 74,\n      \"endLine\": 94,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6231437517740935,\n      \"snippet\": \"- `src/components/AgentTravel.tsx` — Hallway traversal system with L-shaped pathfinding, traveling agent sprites with walking bob animation, collaboration link lines with data-stream pulses\\n- `src/components/TaskFlowSignals.tsx` — Animated task flow packets (SVG circle elements with animateMotion) between rooms\\n- `src/components/Starfield.tsx` — Ambient starfield with 60 twinkling stars and drifting nebula clouds\\n- `src/components/AgentOffice.tsx` — Main orchestrator: live ticker, mood bar, queue pressure indicator, crew status cards, demo mode\\n- `src/components/DoorAnimation.tsx` — Door open/close slide animations with glow edges\\n- `src/components/AmbientStation.tsx` — Ship fly-bys, station\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-05-15.md#L74-L94\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-05-15.md#L74-L94\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"e75b25c424c36397ad9a8c387eaba94db772296c21a9ce5081963d71f3f335db\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 28,\n      \"endLine\": 52,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.5877022905539557,\n      \"snippet\": \"- 2026-05-11 — ZIP extraction failed repeatedly\\n- 2026-05-12 — Andre said to leave it for tomorrow; plan stored in memory\\n\\n## Sources\\n- [[mission-control-dashboard]] — Concept page with full architecture\\n- memory/mission-control-plan.md — Detailed implementation plan\\n\\n## Open Questions\\n- How to fix ZIP extraction (try Python zipfile module?)\\n- Should we use bun or npm?\\n- When will Andre return to this project?\\n\\n## Dashboard Wired (2026-05-12)\\n- Moved from Downloads to `~/mission-control-dashboard/`\\n- Installed bun + 494 dependencies\\n- Replaced all mock data with live OpenClaw data via `createServerFn`\\n- Data sources: tasks.json, openclaw.json (cron), memory/*.md, MEMORY.md, workspace/*.md, p\\n\\nSource: memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md#L28-L52\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/wiki/entities/mission-control.md#L28-L52\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 3357,\n    \"hits\": 6\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"id":"eed19f73ec82653ce8c952ef85504f65d12b9d668dff2058120971994b6d8da5","path":"memory/2026-05-13.md","startLine":1,"endLine":30,"score":1,"textScore":0.6184196983807188,"snippet":"# 2026-05-13 Daily Log (continued)\n\n## Afternoon/Evening Session\n\n### Completed\n- **Dashboard redesign (T-119)** — 3-column layout: Left=live activity feed, Center=Spacestation rooms, Right=quick actions\n- **Task detail panel** — Changed from right-slide to centered modal\n- **Dreaming toggle** — 