,\\n      \\\"wakeMode\\\": \\\"now\\\",\\n      \\\"payload\\\": {\\n        \\\"kind\\\": \\\"agentTurn\\\",\\n        \\\"message\\\": \\\"Run the daily station check and send a Telegram sitrep. Do NOT use any AI model calls — just use shell commands and file operations.\\\\n\\\\n1. **System Health**: Run `sysctl vm.loadavg`, `df -h / | tail -1`, `vm_stat | head -5`, `uptime`. Log results to `memory/health-log.md` with timestamp.\\\\n\\\\n2. **Git Auto-Commit**: Check `cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && git status --porcelain`. If there are changes, run `git add -A && git commit -m \\\\\\\"auto: daily commit\\\\\\\" && git push`. Log result.\\\\n\\\\n3. **Task Cleanup**: Read `data/tasks.json`. Archive any completed tasks older than 30 days to `data/tasks-archive.json`. Log count.\\\\n\\\\n4. **Backup Check**: Check if `/Volumes/OpenClaw-WD` or `/Volumes/Public` is mounted. Check if today's backup file exists. Log result.\\\\n\\\\n5. **Daily Summary**: Append a brief summary to `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` with: date, system health snapshot, git commit status, tasks archived, backup status.\\\\n\\\\n6. **Telegram Sitrep**: Use `curl` to send a one-line daily sitrep to Telegram chat 7507878944 via the OpenClaw gateway message API. The sitrep should include: tasks active count, tasks awaiting review count, disk %, and overall status (nominal/fail). Format example:\\\\n   `📡 DAILY SITREP — 2026-05-16 | 3 active · 1 awaiting review · 85% disk · ✅ ALL SYSTEMS NOMINAL`\\\\n   \\\\n   If disk > 90% or any critical issues found, use `⚠️` instead and note the issue.\\\\n   \\\\n   Use the OpenClaw gateway to send: `openclaw message send --channel telegram --to 7507878944 \\\\\\\"<sitrep text>\\\\\\\"` or use the gateway HTTP API at localhost:18789.\\\\n\\\\nKeep it fast. Use exec for all operations. Do not call any models.\\\",\\n        \\\"timeoutSeconds\\\": 120\\n      },\\n      \\\"delivery\\\": {\\n        \\\"mode\\\": \\\"announce\\\",\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"last\\\",\\n        \\\"to\\\": \\\"7507878944\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"state\\\": {\\n        \\\"nextRunAtMs\\\": 1779400800000,\\n        \\\"lastRunAtMs\\\": 1779314400008,\\n        \\\"lastRunStatus\\\": \\\"ok\\\",\\n        \\\"lastStatus\\\": \\\"ok\\\",\\n        \\\"lastDurationMs\\\": 90984,\\n        \\\"lastDeliveryStatus\\\": \\\"delivered\\\",\\n        \\\"consecutiveErrors\\\": 0,\\n        \\\"consecutiveSkipped\\\": 0,\\n        \\\"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\\\": \\\"not-requested\\\",\\n        \\\"lastDelivered\\\": true\\n      },\\n      \\\"updatedAtMs\\\": 1779314490992\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"total\\\": 1,\\n  \\\"offset\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"limit\\\": 1,\\n  \\\"hasMore\\\": false,\\n  \\\"nextOffset\\\": null,\\n  \\\"deliveryPreviews\\\": {\\n    \\\"dae7406b-ec78-4752-ba93-91bc62541f7d\\\": {\\n      \\\"label\\\": \\\"announce -> telegram:7507878944\\\",\\n      \\\"detail\\\": \\\"resolved from last, session agent:main:telegram:direct:7507878944\\\"\\n    }\\n  }\\n}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"isError\": false,\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392627416,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"ef75d1f0\",\n        \"seq\": 12\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"[assistant turn failed before producing content]\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/owl-alpha\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"error\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392627423,\n      \"errorMessage\": \"429 Provider returned error\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"fc86aa16\",\n        \"seq\": 13\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Only one active session (this one) and one cron job (Daily Station Check at 23:00). No other sessions or sub-agents running.\\n\\nI'm not seeing a \\\"main control UI\\\" job running. Could you give me more detail? When you say \\\"the main control UI was doing a job\\\" — do you mean:\\n\\n- The **Mission Control Dashboard** (the Vite app on port 3000) was processing something?\\n- A **cron job or automated task** you kicked off from the dashboard?\\n- A **sub-agent or background task** spawned from the UI?\\n\\nAlso, what kind of \\\"live updates of live chat\\\" did you want? I can:\\n- **Stream session activity** — notify you when agents/tasks complete\\n- **Push dashboard state changes** — forward agent office updates to this chat\\n- **Monitor the Telegram session** — relay messages between sessions\\n\\nGive me a bit more context and I'll set it up.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/owl-alpha\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392630130,\n      \"responseId\": \"gen-1779392630-nTUybbagGDdh3Ac7rmIt\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"e8898430\",\n        \"seq\": 14\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"⚠️ Something went wrong while processing your request. Please try again, or use /new to start a fresh session.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openclaw\",\n      \"model\": \"delivery-mirror\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392662724,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"02cd5701-ed12-4330-a898-660dfa141560\",\n        \"seq\": 15\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Conversation context (untrusted, chronological, selected for current message):\\n#1746 Thu 2026-05-21 20:08 GMT+1 Andre: We back\\n#1748 Thu 2026-05-21 20:23 GMT+1 Andre: Can you send live updates of live chat\\n#1750 Thu 2026-05-21 20:43 GMT+1 Andre: The main control ui was doing a job, can you feedback if this is done from the main chat session\\n\\nHuh\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392792483,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"02d25e72\",\n        \"seq\": 16\n      },\n      \"senderLabel\": \"Andre (7507878944)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"\\n\\nSorry, I think I overcomplicated my earlier responses. Let me re-read what you're actually asking.\\n\\nYou're saying: the Mission Control Dashboard (the main control UI) was running some job/task, and you want me to check on its status and report back here in this Telegram chat. And more broadly, you want me to send live updates from the dashboard to this chat as things happen.\\n\\nLet me check what the dashboard is up to right now.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/owl-alpha\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392792494,\n      \"responseId\": \"gen-1779392792-xMcSOnLoELGvAGxjRBqP\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"8106d390\",\n        \"seq\": 17\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"toolResult\",\n      \"toolCallId\": \"bf58f402-5525-4880-ad3d-f405a1d165f4\",\n      \"toolName\": \"exec\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\n        }\n      ],\n      \"isError\": false,\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392817140,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"914fb211\",\n        \"seq\": 23\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"[assistant turn failed before producing content]\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/owl-alpha\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"error\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392817142,\n      \"errorMessage\": \"429 Provider returned error\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"de42812a\",\n        \"seq\": 24\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"OK so the dashboard is running on port 3000, but there's no `/api/health` route (returned 404). The `data/` directory is empty — no `tasks.json`. And there are no other sessions or sub-agents running.\\n\\nBased on what I can see:\\n\\n- **Dashboard**: ✅ Running (port 3000, build `7fd8001`, last commit 16/05/2026)\\n- **No active jobs/tasks**: No `tasks.json`, no sub-agents, no sessions beyond this chat\\n- **Only cron**: Daily Station Check at 23:00 (last ran successfully, next run tonight)\\n\\nI don't see evidence of the \\\"main control UI doing a job\\\" — at least nothing active right now. The dashboard looks idle.\\n\\nWhen you say you wanted \\\"live updates of live chat\\\" — did you mean you wanted the dashboard to show this Telegram conversation? Or did you want me to forward dashboard activity to this chat? Want me to wire something up?\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"openrouter\",\n      \"model\": \"openrouter/owl-alpha\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1779392819880,\n      \"responseId\": \"gen-1779392820-PPPZcKNrBGkx1vQtat4W\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"51c38cb8\",\n        \"seq\": 25\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"⚠️ Something went wrong while processing your request. Please try again, or use /new to start a fresh session.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-responses\",\n      \"provider\": \"openclaw\",\n